We are one of the leading technology groups in Italy. We operate as a Business & Technology Accelerator for companies, financial institutions, and public sector organizations, supporting the evolution of their IT and digital strategies. Through an ecosystem of companies that share values, business strategies, and a common vision, we enable our clients to unlock the full potential of technology, amplifying its positive impact on both the economy and society.
What To Expect
The Backend Developer will operate within a business unit specializing in managed services and Cloud-based solutions. The role is part of a division focused on delivering innovative solutions for multi-utility organizations. The position involves designing and developing modern applications aimed at improving digitalization and operational efficiency in essential services.
What You Will Do
Design, develop, and maintain applications using .NET Framework and .NET;
Design, develop, and execute Unit Tests to ensure code quality;
Support the implementation and optimization of data management solutions;
Optimize and enhance existing applications;
Develop reusable code and shared libraries;
Contribute to infrastructure and DevOps-related activities;
Collaborate with Project Managers, Architects, and team members to ensure successful project delivery.
What We Expect From You
Diploma or degree in Computer Science or related technical fields;
Experience with .NET Framework 4.6+ and/or .NET Core (version 6 or later) using C#;
Experience with Web development technologies (ASP.NET MVC, ASP.NET WebApi);
Experience with Infrastructure and/or Cloud environments, preferably Microsoft Azure;
Knowledge of relational databases, T-SQL, and Entity Framework (or similar ORM frameworks);
Familiarity with code versioning tools (GitHub, Mercurial, or equivalents);
Understanding of main design patterns;
Ability to work with a results-oriented approach and meet project objectives.
Preferred Qualifications: Experience with DevOps practices, Knowledge of Python, Docker and Kubernetes.
Strong problem-solving abilities; Proactive approach; Ability to mentor junior team members; Flexibility and motivation in handling assigned tasks.

